<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SNS運用代行管理システム</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    
    .hero-section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 5px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .hero-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
      animation: float 20s infinite linear;
    }
    
    @keyframes float {
      0% { transform: translateX(-100%) rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: translateX(100%) rotate(360deg); }
    }
    
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    
    .companies-section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    
    .company-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    
    .company-card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fafc 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
      cursor: pointer;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .company-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1), transparent);
      transition: left 0.6s;
    }
    
    .company-card:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }
    
    .company-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.25);
      transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0f9ff 100%);
    }
    
    .company-name {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .company-industry {
      color: #667eea;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .company-details {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .detail-label {
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .detail-value {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    
    .company-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 3px;
      flex-wrap: nowrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .btn-compact {
      padding: 5px 10px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
      font-weight: 600;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
      min-width: 0;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    
    .btn-compact::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
      transition: left 0.5s;
    }
    
    .btn-compact:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }
    
    .btn-data {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #34d399 100%);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn-data:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #10b981 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.6);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .btn-analytics {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #6366f1 100%);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn-analytics:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #4f46e5 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.6);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-report {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9f7aea 0%, #a78bfa 100%);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(159, 122, 234, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn-report:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #9333ea 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(159, 122, 234, 0.6);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-edit {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #f97316 100%);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn-edit:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d97706 0%, #ea580c 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.6);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .empty-state {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .empty-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .empty-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    
    .empty-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .system-management {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0f9ff 100%);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
    }
    
    .management-title {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    
    .management-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-section">
      <h1 class="hero-title">SNS運用代行管理システム</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">クライアント企業の選択</p>
      
      <!-- メインナビゲーションボタン -->
      <div class="main-navigation" style="margin-top: 30px; display: flex; gap: 15px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/companies/add" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 1rem;">🏢 新規企業登録</a>
        <a href="/companies" class="btn btn-info" style="padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 1rem;">📋 クライアント管理</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <main>
      <div class="companies-section">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">クライアント企業</h2>
        </div>
        
        <% if (companies && companies.length > 0) { %>
          <div class="company-grid">
            <% companies.forEach(company => { %>
              <div class="company-card" onclick="window.location.href='/companies/<%= company.id %>'">
                <div class="company-name"><%= company.company_name %></div>
                <div class="company-industry"><%= company.industry %></div>
                
                <div class="company-details">
                  <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">運用開始</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= company.start_date %></span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">開始時フォロワー</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= company.initial_followers.toLocaleString() %></span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">ID</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= company.id %></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="company-actions" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">
                  <a href="/add-post-grid?company=<%= company.id %>" class="btn-compact btn-data">📊 データ入力</a>
                  <a href="/analytics?company=<%= company.id %>" class="btn-compact btn-analytics">📈 分析</a>
                  <a href="/report/<%= company.id %>" class="btn-compact btn-report">📋 レポート</a>
                  <a href="/companies/edit/<%= company.id %>" class="btn-compact btn-edit">✏️ 編集</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="empty-state">
            <div class="empty-icon">🏢</div>
            <h3 class="empty-title">登録されたクライアントがありません</h3>
            <p class="empty-description">
              まずはSNS運用代行を行うクライアント企業の情報を登録してください。<br>
              企業情報にはSNS運用開始日や開始時のフォロワー数などを記録できます。
            </p>
            <a href="/companies/add" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">最初のクライアントを登録する</a>
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

</body>
</html>